urchased by drivers through a web-based tool. There they can also view where, when, how much (gallon and dollar amounts) and who transacted so you can account for every penny. &nbsp;</font></p></blockquote><p style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><font face="arial"><br></font></p><p><font style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;" face="arial" size="3"><font size="3">Because of your membership in&nbsp;</font></font><font face="arial">{!Opportunity.IS_Lead_Program_Interest__c}&nbsp;</font><span class="Apple-tab-span" style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt; white-space: pre;"><font face="arial">we are able to get you rebates ranging form<b> 3.5 to 4.5 cents</b> off per gallon at ExxonMobil stations for the life of the program.   </font></span><font style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;">If you have any questions feel free to contact me directly.</font></p><p style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><font face="arial" size="3"><br></font></p><p style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><font face="arial" size="3">If you want to go ahead with the program,</font><font face="arial" size="3">&nbsp;email&nbsp;or fax the completed application attached</font><font face="arial" size="3">. &nbsp;Otherwise, I will follow up in the next few days to get your thoughts and help with any questions.</font></p><p style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><font face="arial"><br></font></p><p style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><font face="arial"><br></font></p><p style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><font face="arial">Brian Fitzpatrick</font></p><p style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><font face="arial">Fuel Service Specialist&nbsp;</font></p><p style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><font face="arial